r.", "\u2013 Og s\u00e5 er det koselig at de som ikke kj\u00f8per skolemat ogs\u00e5 sitter her sammen med oss, mener de."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sainntja"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c1091daee9ce4b469e601fb73fb3a816a62a6d0efbd4c9f2c28fbe80e6c977b6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-17T10:39:17.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Elevene p\u00e5 Strindheim st\u00e5r i k\u00f8 for \u00e5 f\u00e5 frukt etter lunsjen. Her er det en naturlig del av skoledagen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1188918.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/skolefrukt1"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/cbbe5d01ba948a21a15b3b8c46743d3b7981b8b6.jpg?59931b97"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Frukt er sunt og godt -adressa.no", "Frukt hver dag", "Koselig m\u00e5ltid"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "cbbe5d01ba948a21a15b3b8c46743d3b7981b8b6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sainntja"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "frukt"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["strindheim", "bama"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["vegard holm alsvik", "sofie eidissen lj\u00f8kjell", "bente vik", "maria forbord helland"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sainntja"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1188918.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/skolefrukt1"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value